此地下車站於1932年9月10日啟用<ref name=Chambers/><ref name="Opening">{{cite news|last1=Crowell|first1=Paul|title=Gay Midnight Crowd Rides First Trains In The New Subway: Throngs at Station an Hour Before Time, Rush Turnstiles When Chains are Dropped|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9507E2D61231E633A25753C1A96F9C946394D6CF|accessdate=8 November 2015|publisher=New York Times|date=September 10, 1932|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407053840/https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9507E2D61231E633A25753C1A96F9C946394D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>，設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道。由於位處山丘以下因此深入地底。實際上，曼哈頓島最高的天然點為{{link-en|布尼特公園 (紐約)|Bennett Park (New York)|布尼特公園}}，位於此站介乎西183街及185街與{{link-en|華盛頓堡大道 (曼哈頓)|Fort Washington Avenue (Manhattan)|華盛頓堡大道}}的出口旁邊（該處沒有西184街）。

由於車站的深度，只能設扶手電梯前往南端的181街以及升降機前往北端的布尼特公園出口。升降機過去只在日間營運，並要求付費使用<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1939/08/07/94707478.html?pageNumber=13|title=FREE ELEVATORS IN SUBWAY FOUGHT|last=|first=|date=August 7, 1939|work=|newspaper=The New York Times|page=13|access-date=July 29, 2016|via=}}</ref>。自1957年起，升降機可由來往布尼特大道和華盛頓堡大道的行人使用而不需付費，而在上一站[[190街車站_(IND第八大道線)|190街車站]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1957/09/06/93216229.html?pageNumber=19|title=2 IND ELEVATORS OPEN TO FREE USE|last=|first=|date=September 6, 1957|website=nytimes.com|publisher=The New York Times|page=19|access-date=2016-07-30}}</ref>以及[[IRT百老匯-第七大道線|IRT百老匯-第七大道線]]的[[191街車站_(IRT百老匯-第七大道線)|191街車站]]亦有同樣情況<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/12/nyregion/washington-heights-journal-a-subway-passageway-just-for-the-courageous.html|title=Washington Heights Journal; A Subway Passageway Just for the Courageous|last=Kurtz|first=Josh|date=1991-08-12|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-07-30|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117065249/https://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/12/nyregion/washington-heights-journal-a-subway-passageway-just-for-the-courageous.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

